        <mxCell id="D9f-itHjY20SfIZD133B-1" parent="1" style="strokeWidth=2;html=1;shape=mxgraph.flowchart.document2;whiteSpace=wrap;size=0.25;fillColor=#1ba1e2;fontColor=#ffffff;strokeColor=#006EAF;" value="Stardeck&#39;s essentials-first system architecture ensures its capabilities as a minimalist Raspberry Pi cyberdeck that prioritizes portable computing, local file management, and distraction-free terminal workflows.&amp;nbsp;Modular architecture allows future integration of custom keyboards, GPIO accessories, and additional storage peripherals." vertex="1">
